abstract: K J Choi and Scott Brown share third-round lead at Farmers Insurance Open golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: K. J. Choi one-putted his final six holes to salvage an even-par 72 and a share of the lead with Scott Brown going into the final round of the Farmers Insurance Open in San Diego.

headline.print_headline: Two Share Lead in San Diego
